Title: mk_oracle: Fixed problems with multiple ORACLE_HOME entries on Grid setups
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1608109967
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

A Oracle Grid setup may contain more than one {{ORACLE_HOME}} entries. Until
now {{mk_oracle}} was not aware, that this could be the case and took all of
them. Now only the first entry will be considered.
